    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>Hii testes probant <rs key="#Abbots">abbatem</rs>
                        <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/1460"><placeName ref="#places/4179"
                                >Pomposianum</placeName></orgName> possedisse <rs key="#Churches"
                            >ecclesiam</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Churches" ref="#juridical_persons/3666"><placeName
                                ref="#places/4895">Fane</placeName></orgName> per XL annos quiete
                        antequam <rs key="#Bishops">episcopus</rs>
                        <persName key="#Bishops">
                            <name ref="Gervichus">Gervichus</name></persName> intraret, sciliced <rs
                            key="#Priests">presbiter</rs>
                        <persName key="#Witness #Priests">
                            <name ref="Lauriscius">Lauriscius</name></persName>, presbiter <persName
                            key="#Witness #Priests">
                            <name ref="Iohanens de Basilica">Iohannes de Basilica</name>
                        </persName>. Quod <persName key="#Witness">
                            <name ref="Inzo">Inzo</name></persName> nam idem facit mentionem de <persName>
                            <name ref="Huuarnari Maior">Guarnerio maiore</name></persName>,
                            <persName key="#Witness">
                            <name ref="Marolfus">Marolus</name></persName>. Isti alii probant quod
                        possedit abbas Pomposie per XXX annos antequam Gervichus intraret,
                        s(cilicet) <persName key="#Witness #Abbots">
                            <name ref="Marcus">Marcus</name></persName> abbas de <orgName
                            ref="#juridical_persons/3656">Vidore</orgName>, <persName key="#Witness">
                            <name ref="Dominicus de Methone">Dominicus de Methone</name></persName>,
                        s(cilicet) <persName key="#Witness">
                            <name ref="Conus de Fana">Conus de Fana</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness">
                            <name ref="Huuarnari de Fana">Guarnerius de Fana</name></persName>. Isti
                        alii probant abbatem possedisse antequam episcopus Gervicus intraret aut per
                        X annos aut octo aut aliquo tempore ante, s(cilicet) <persName
                            key="#Witness #Other_minor_officer">Fredericus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Other_minor_officer">senescalcus</rs>, presbiter <persName
                            key="#Witness #Priests">
                            <name ref="Bertram">Bertrammus</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness">
                            <name ref="Azolinus">Azellus</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness">
                            <name ref="Ardemannus">Ardimanus</name></persName>,<persName
                            key="#Witness">
                            <name ref="Adam">Adam</name></persName>. Isti probant de ieccionem
                        factam ab episcopo Geroicho, s(cilicet) presbiter Bertrammus ubi dicit quod
                        episcopus presbiteros qui stabant pro abbate expulit, s(cilicet) presbiter
                        Laurisius ubi(a) dicit quod episcopus intravit, et <persName key="#Witness">
                            <name ref="Iohannes de Balega">Iohannes de Balega</name></persName> ubi
                        dicit quod intravit, <persName key="#Witness">
                            <name ref="Petrus">Petrus</name></persName> ubi dicit quod intravit
                        episcopus. Marolus idem de ieccione, Azellus idem de ieccione, Conus de Fana
                        idem de ieccione ubi dicit quod episcopus intromisit. Isti probant quod <rs
                            key="#Value">pecunia</rs> fuit data pro expensis litis iussu iudicum,
                        s(cilicet) Adam, presbiter Bertrammus. Testes vero sui non contradicunt
                        nobis quia loqantur in spiritualibus sed solus Gervichus qui per vim
                        intravit habuit [â€¦]. Si vero esset contrarii nostri, debent credi quia
                        antiquiores sunt et nobiliores et d(icu)nt vera vel verisimilia et quia
                        adiuvantur cartula nostra antiqua et quia sumus possessores et in dubiis pro
                        possessore iudicatur et debetis magis credere quod pecunia fuit data ex
                        causa honesta quam inhonesta et propter personas iudicantium et personis
                        transigentium. Et insuper dominus papa eodem anno confirmavit transactionem
                        et ipse episcopus Ionathas in iure fuit confessus, quod Guarnerius maior
                        avus istius Guarnerii dedit ea ecclesiam Pomposie quem Gua(rnerium)
                        confitemur dedisse possessiones et instrumentum quod ostendimus.</ab>
